name: instance
description: The multitudinous of the items represents the number of us human individual. The lines in each item are our talents, gift, skills, IQ and etc. some of us have more some of us less the more lines the more the shape looks like a circle. Each is moving toward perfection. To be a perfect circle like the on in the center. Some can get very close to that but can never touch perfection (the Platonic reality). Colors are our qualities. combination of all colors turns into white but none of the individuals can have enough to be as white as the perfect circle in the middle. This is all distributed randomly. Just like our lives. We have access to random resources. We have random talents, etc...
